{
  "uid": "loadgen-search-sync",
  "title": "Loadgen Search Sync Lag",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "tags": ["loadgen", "v2", "search-sync"],
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": {"from": "now-30m", "to": "now"},
  "templating": {"list": []},
  "annotations": {"list": []},
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Search-Sync Lag Scenario",
      "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Canonical → Elasticsearch indexing lag\n\nMetrics from the `search-sync-lag` scenario: `loadgen_search_index_lag_seconds` (histogram) and `loadgen_search_index_visible_total{outcome=...}` (counter). The reference line at 30s on the lag panels marks the Elasticsearch default `refresh_interval` — a p50 near 30–40s is normal."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "title": "Search-index lag p50 / p99",
      "description": "Canonical-to-Elasticsearch indexing lag percentiles from loadgen_search_index_lag_seconds. The 30s reference line marks the ES default refresh_interval; p50 should sit close to that, p99 should stay below ~60s (2× refresh).",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 3},
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "line"}
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 30},
              {"color": "red", "value": 60}
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "p50"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "blue", "mode": "fixed"}}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "p99"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "orange", "mode": "fixed"}}]
          }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(loadgen_search_index_lag_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(loadgen_search_index_lag_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "title": "Visible outcomes rate — by outcome",
      "description": "Stacked rate of terminal outcomes from loadgen_search_index_visible_total. outcome=visible is the success path; timeout/transport_error/publish_error indicate SUT problems; dropped_inflight indicates the scenario itself is misconfigured (rate × timeout > MaxInFlight).",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 3},
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 30,
            "stacking": {"mode": "normal", "group": "A"}
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "visible"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "green", "mode": "fixed"}}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "timeout"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "yellow", "mode": "fixed"}}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "transport_error"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed"}}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "publish_error"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "orange", "mode": "fixed"}}]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "dropped_inflight"},
            "properties": [{"id": "color", "value": {"fixedColor": "purple", "mode": "fixed"}}]
          }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (outcome)(rate(loadgen_search_index_visible_total[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{outcome}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "title": "Dropped-inflight total",
      "description": "Cumulative count of dropped_inflight outcomes. Any value > 0 indicates the scenario shed work because MaxInFlight was saturated — the run is misconfigured (rate × timeout > MaxInFlight). Large red number is a louder-than-it-looks signal.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 11},
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "colorMode": "background"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "red", "value": 1}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(loadgen_search_index_visible_total{outcome=\"dropped_inflight\"})",
          "legendFormat": "dropped_inflight",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "title": "Transport-error total",
      "description": "Cumulative NATS transport failures when polling search-service. Any sustained increase signals search-service unreachability or a subject misroute.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 11},
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "colorMode": "background"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": null},
              {"color": "orange", "value": 1}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(loadgen_search_index_visible_total{outcome=\"transport_error\"})",
          "legendFormat": "transport_error",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "stat",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "title": "Visible / total ratio",
      "description": "Fraction of search-sync attempts that observed visibility (outcome=visible). A healthy run sits near 1.0; ratios below 0.95 indicate timeouts, transport errors, or scenario misconfiguration are eating into the success rate.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 11},
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]},
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "colorMode": "background"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {"color": "red", "value": null},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.9},
              {"color": "green", "value": 0.95}
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(loadgen_search_index_visible_total{outcome=\"visible\"}) / sum(loadgen_search_index_visible_total)",
          "legendFormat": "visible ratio",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus"},
      "title": "Lag histogram — per-bucket rate (heatmap-style)",
      "description": "Rate of lag observations per histogram bucket. Useful for spotting the bimodal 'before vs after ES refresh' distribution: a healthy run shows a peak in the 25–35s buckets (just past refresh_interval) and a much smaller tail past 60s. Two peaks or a heavy right tail suggest indexing pressure.",
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 15},
      "options": {
        "legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"},
        "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "custom": {"lineWidth": 1}
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(loadgen_search_index_lag_seconds_bucket[1m])) by (le)",
          "legendFormat": "le={{le}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
